moduleMetadataJson.name: Windows Executable Download and Evaluate VBS
moduleMetadataJson.description:
Downloads a file from an HTTP(S) URL and executes it as a vbs script.
            Use it to stage a vbs encoded payload from a short command line.
author: scriptjunkie

options.description: An initial script to run on session creation (before AutoRunScript)
